<div class="sidebar">
	<h4>POPULAR POSTS</h4>

	<ul class="menu-list">
		<% Post.most_popular.each do |post| %>
			<li><%= link_to post.title, post %></li>
		<% end %>
	</ul>

	<h4>COMPARE CAMPING GEAR</h4>

	<ul class="menu-list">
		<% Category.all.order(:name).each do |category| %>
			<% if category.gears.count > 10 %>
				<li><%= link_to "#{category.name} (#{category.gears.count})", category %></li>
			<% end %>
		<% end %>
	</ul>

	<h4>ABOUT</h4>
	My name is Stu, and this is Ten Pound Backpack, the focus of which is to help your backpack weigh less so that you can enjoy the outdoors more.<br><br>
	The most important part of the website is the <div class="btn-group dropdown"><a role="button" id="dropdownMenu2" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="true">
    Gear Lists</a>
  <ul class="dropdown-menu" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenu2">
    <% Category.all.each do |category| %>
      <% if category.gears.count > 10 %>
        <li><%= link_to category.name, category_path(category) %></li>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </ul></div>, but there's plenty more to help you find that perfect piece of backpacking gear.<br><br>
	<p>As for me, I'm in the 20s, love backpacking and call BC, Canada home. I'm always happy to get emails if you want to know more.

	<h4>BLOG POST CATEGORIES</h4>

	<ul class="menu-list">
		<% PostCategory.all.order(:name).each do |category| %>
			<li><%= link_to "#{category.name} (#{category.posts.count})", category %></li>
		<% end %>
	</ul>

	<h4>CONTACT</h4>
	<%= link_to "Contact Us", contact_path %>
</div>